quests.desc: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! Here is how to play! First of all, you could, like, make an effort to take a trip north. And then, try to head west. Then, venture north. And then, venture west. And then, travel south. Then, make an effort to venture south. And then, go to the south. Okay, and then, make an effort to venture east. And then, try to move north. Okay, and then, pick-up the pair of headphones from the floor of the spare room. Got that? Good!

objective: Welcome to another profound session of TextWorld! Here is your task for today. First off, if it's not too much trouble, I need you to try to go north. Then, try to venture west. Okay, and then, try to move north. With that over with, make an effort to venture west. And then, make an attempt to go south. With that over with, head south. Once you succeed at that, make an effort to take a trip south. Then, take a trip east. Then, attempt to go to the north. After that, pick up the pair of headphones from the floor of the spare room. That's it!
